<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<h2>Data Collection and Usage</h2>

<p>At EarlyVisionAI, we are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring the security of your personal information. This privacy policy outlines our practices concerning the collection, use, and protection of your data.</p>

<h3>No Data Storage</h3>
<p>We want to assure you that we do not store any of the data you provide for analysis. Our service is designed to perform one-time, on-demand analyses without retaining your information.</p>

<h3>One-Time Analysis</h3>
<p>When you use our service:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Your data is processed in real-time for the sole purpose of providing you with the requested analysis.</li>
    <li>Once the analysis is complete and the results are delivered to you, we immediately and permanently delete all associated data from our systems.</li>
    <li>We do not retain, sell, share, or use your data for any purpose other than the specific analysis you request.</li>
</ul>

<h3>Data Security</h3>
<p>While your data is being processed:</p>
<ul>
    <li>We employ industry-standard security measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure.</li>
    <li>All data transmissions between your device and our servers are encrypted using SSL/TLS protocols.</li>
    <li>Access to our systems is strictly limited to authorized personnel who require it to perform their duties.</li>
</ul>

<h3>User Responsibilities</h3>
<p>To ensure the best protection of your data:</p>
<ul>
    <li>We recommend not submitting any sensitive personal information that is not necessary for the analysis.</li>
    <li>You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of any account credentials or access tokens provided to you.</li>
</ul>

<h3>Changes to This Policy</h3>
<p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with a revised effective date. We encourage you to review this policy periodically to stay informed about how we protect your privacy.</p>

<h3>Contact Us</h3>
<p>If you have any questions or concerns about our privacy practices, please contact us at [contact email or form].</p>

